{"title":"Leatt 3.0 Enduro Convertible Helmet Snaps-On Protection: Full-Face, 3/4, or Just Your Head","link":"https://bikerumor.com/leatt-3-0-enduro-convertible-helmet-snaps-on-protection-full-face-3-4-or-just-your-head/","date":1686664830000,"content":"<p>Leatt’s new 3.0 Enduro Helmet is one lid to rule them all. Want a simple half-shell, fine. Feel like you need a bit more all-mountain coverage to pair with a set of goggles, just snap in the ear guards. Need full-on enduro protection for racing or a trip to the bikepark, just pop the ears off and snap a chin bar in its place for a proper full-face.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Leatt 3.0 Enduro Helmet: convertible half-shell, 3/4 &amp; full-face</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, portreait with bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_with-goggles-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>photos c. Leatt</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We actually got a sneak peek at the new Leatt 3.0 Enduro Helmet first last summer, then a bit more detail at the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2023-leatt-adds-hydradri-foul-weather-gear-new-head-knee-protection-more-womens-kit/\" target=\"_blank\">start of this year</a>. Taking their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/leatt-4-0-enduro-helmet-with-removable-chinbar-delivers-dh-certified-protection/\" target=\"_blank\">convertible MTB 4.0 Enduro full-face</a> helmet to the next level, the new 3.0 adds a third mode in-between half shell &amp; full face – a 3/4 protection helmet with removable ear guards. And surprisingly, it does so at a lower price-point.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, trial riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_trail-riding-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new 3-in-1 design “<em>can be worn as a half shell open face helmet for light trail riding, or in the jet style with the addition of the over-the-ear guards for added coverage, or clip on the full chin bar for maximum protection. One helmet, three levels of protection for any trail.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>But why?</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side.jpg\"><img width=\"2400\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side.jpg\" alt=\"Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, convertible half-shell, three-quarter-shell full-face mountain bike helmet, 3-in-1 detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side.jpg 2400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side-297x84.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side-800x225.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side-120x34.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side-768x216.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side-1536x432.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_3-in-1-side-2048x576.jpg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption><em>photo by Cory Benson, c. Bikerumor</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The convertible 4.0 was already popular with enduro riders who could remove the chin bar for climbing transitions, then pop it back into place for racing stages. But there are a lot of times in between where you might not feel the need for full-face protection. In between a bit of extra over-the-ears security will make you feel more confident picking technical lines, and matches up nicely with a pair of goggles for wraparound protection, while keeping air flow to your mouth and nose unobstructed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Leatt 3.0 Enduro then is the happy medium, where you can customize your coverage depending on how you feel, and what the conditions warrant. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, convertible half-shell, three-quarter-shell full-face mountain bike helmet, push-button detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_push-button-lock-detail-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>photo by Cory Benson, c. Bikerumor</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Just press the easier-to-use push-button system to securely add or remove the ear guards or chin bar.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, POwerbridge inside\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_powerbridge-internal-reinforcement-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new helmet features a standard in-mold polycarbonate shell over EPS foam for protection, adding a Powerbridge internal reinforcement at the top of the helmet for better impact force distribution.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside.jpg\" alt=\"Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, convertible half-shell, three-quarter-shell full-face mountain bike helmet, 360 Turbine tech detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell-three-quarter-shell-full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_360-Turbine-tech-inside-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>photo by Cory Benson, c. Bikerumor</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Like other Leatt helmets, the new convertible 3.0 Enduro features 360° Turbine Tech pads to help absorb energy, reduce brain rotational acceleration, and isolate non-linear impacts. It gets top-tier dial retention at the back, and a premium Fidlock magnetic buckle for easy one-handed claspin, plus an adjustable visor and a sunglasses docking port in its upper rear vents.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, chin bar detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_chin-bar-ear-guards-detail-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Just like the 4.0, the Leatt 3.0 Enduro gets an ASTM DH-certified chin bar so you can be sure of the highest level of protection when you need it. And the base open-face half-shell is AS/NZS, EN &amp; CPSC certified on its own. It doesn’t appear there’s any specific middle-ground certification for when the ear guards are installed.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, exploded\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_exploded-view-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The half-shell alone is said to weigh just 360g, while adding the chin bar brings it up to 700g.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Leatt 3.0 Enduro – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, contents\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_contents-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Leatt 3.0 Enduro helmet sells for $270 / 290€ including both the removable ear guards and chin bar, as standard. Ride it however you feel most comfortable, depending on the trail. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side.jpg\"><img width=\"1700\" height=\"1700\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, stealth\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side.jpg 1700w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_all-black-full-left-side-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_white-full-face-angled.jpg\"><img width=\"1700\" height=\"1700\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_white-full-face-angled.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, white\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_white-full-face-angled.jpg 1700w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_white-full-face-angled-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-L