ertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Titanium-ear-guards-angled-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Titanium-ear-guards-angled-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Titanium-ear-guards-angled-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side.jpg\"><img width=\"1700\" height=\"1700\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, pine\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side.jpg 1700w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_Pine-full-face-right-side-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 3.0 Enduro helmet comes in all-black, black &amp; white, grey &amp; black, and red with pine green with red detailing, in 3 sizes (S51-55, M 55-59 &amp; L 59-63cm).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime.jpg\" alt=\"2023 Leatt 3 Enduro MTB Helmet, a convertible half-shell, 3/4-shell, or full-face mountain bike helmet, all-in-1, riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023-Leatt-3-Enduro-MTB-Helmet_convertible-half-shell_three-quarter-shell_full-face-mountain-bike-helmet_airtime-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There’s also a Leatt 2.0 Enduro version of the same exact convertible full-face helmet, minus the Fidlock buckle, sold a bit cheaper without the new ear guards.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://leatt.com/int/explore-mtb\" target=\"_blank\">Leatt.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/leatt-3-0-enduro-convertible-helmet-snaps-on-protection-full-face-3-4-or-just-your-head/\">Leatt 3.0 Enduro Convertible Helmet Snaps-On Protection: Full-Face, 3/4, or Just Your Head</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"18274e8d2e9db9dd25760c568529af043a6e8a5769781f90468eb9134ed500ca","category":"Cycling"}